snippet.title: Warhaven - Official Extended Trailer | gamescom 2023
snippet.description:
One person against the king and a pile of bodies on the journey to revenge. Check out the brutal, extended trailer for Warhaven, the upcoming medieval fantasy brawler game coming to Steam on September 21, 2023.'
